## Step 8 — Enemy AI: Ice Sliding in `ai.ts`

**File:** `/Users/dvolz/Sites/dv-astro/src/game/shark-thief/ai.ts`

`resolveSlide` is defined in `engine.ts` and is not exported. You have two choices:

**Option A (recommended):** Move `resolveSlide` to its own file `slide.ts` and
export it. Import it in both `engine.ts` and `ai.ts`. This avoids a circular import
(`ai.ts` imports from `engine.ts` and `engine.ts` already imports from `ai.ts` —
that is a circular dependency and will break at runtime).

