            <span class="depth-rule-key">SHARK SCORE</span>
            <span class="depth-rule-val">SCORE² ÷ TIME (sec). Doubling your score quadruples it. Cutting time in half doubles it.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="depth-rule-row">
            <span class="depth-rule-key">TOTAL TIME</span>
            <span class="depth-rule-val">Wall-clock seconds from game start until death.</span>
          </div>

          <details class="depth-details">
