              <div class="depth-rule-row">
                <span class="depth-rule-key">ENEMIES</span>
                <span class="depth-rule-val">Every coin you grab spawns a new enemy — the board gets harder fast. Pick coins deliberately, not greedily.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="depth-rule-row">
                <span class="depth-rule-key">CORAL</span>
                <span class="depth-rule-val">At Depth 2, coral barriers are permanent. Plan routes before the board fills up.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="depth-rule-row">
                <span class="depth-rule-key">EFFICIENCY</span>
                <span class="depth-rule-val">Shark Score rewards points AND speed. Being efficient beats grinding a high score slowly.</span>
              </div>
              <div class="depth-rule-row">
                <span class="depth-rule-key">PATHING</span>
                <span class="depth-rule-val">Enemies step toward you every 2 moves — move laterally, not straight back. A perpendicular escape creates angles; a straight retreat compresses the gap.</span>
